      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TREBLE BEERS (5) is struggling to break through but racing consistently, finishing in the minors four starts on end. Last time out flew the lids with a fast early sectional but gathered in and finished in the minors when second (30.26) at this track over 525m. Top prospect. ILLUMINATOR (2) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (30.43) at this track behind Cash In View in a Free For All. Settled off speed and worked to the line nicely. Expected to be in the finish again. UNACCEPTABLE NIK (7) found the going tougher last start when finishing 7th over 515m at Sandown. Scored at Sandown in weaker company the previous run. Strong form has emerged from her last run. One of the main contenders. IVORY NARWHAL (1) cannot be underestimated.",
